lead_paragraph: John Tavares scored twice and Anders Lee got a power-play goal 5:23 into the third period to lift the New York Islanders over the Columbus Blue Jackets 4-3 Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Lee Scores in 3rd Period to Lift Islanders Over Jackets 4-3
